OL,3,C'They feel safer in prison': Homeless
OL,4,Cpeople turning to crime to secure
OL,5,Cshelter
OL,7,FA meeting to discuss ways to deal with
OL,8,Fthe rising number of homeless people
OL,9,Fhas heard that some are turning to
OL,10,Fcrime so they can be sheltered in
OL,11,Fcustody overnight.
OL,13,FPaul McCusker from The People's
OL,14,FKitchen said it is because "they feel
OL,15,Fsafer in prison".
