OL,3,C'They feel safer in prison': Homeless
OL,4,Cpeople turning to crime to secure
OL,5,Cshelter
OL,7,FHe said: "That's quite a sad
OL,8,Freflection on society when people are
OL,9,Factually having to commit crime to go
OL,10,Fto prison because they can't access
OL,11,Faccommodation, and that's the reality
OL,12,Fthat we're dealing with every single
OL,13,Fday."
OL,15,FThe meeting was held in Belfast City
OL,16,FHall and organised by Sinn Fein MLA
OL,17,FCaral Ni Chuilin.
