OL,3,C'They feel safer in prison': Homeless
OL,4,Cpeople turning to crime to secure
OL,5,Cshelter
OL,7,FAmong the issues discussed were claims
OL,8,Fthat a number of people did not
OL,9,Freceive emergency accommodation during
OL,10,Ffreezing temperatures at the beginning
OL,11,Fof the month.
OL,13,FPreviously, when speaking to UTV,
OL,14,FGrainia Long from the Housing
OL,15,FExecutive said that she could
OL,16,F"absolutely assure offers" of
OL,17,Faccommodation were made.
