OL,3,C'They feel safer in prison': Homeless
OL,4,Cpeople turning to crime to secure
OL,5,Cshelter
OL,7,FIn response to Ni Chuilin's comments,
OL,8,Fthe Housing Executive said they
OL,9,Fwelcomed Thursday's meeting and in
OL,10,Fparticular they addressed the Severe
OL,11,FWeather Emergency Protocol (SWEP)
OL,12,Fwhich they claim is ''not a statutory
OL,13,Fduty'' but which, they ''proactively
OL,14,Fenact'' .
