OL,7,FThe statement also said: ''While one
OL,8,Fof the SWEP providers did face
OL,9,Fcapacity challenges on the night of
OL,10,Fthe 4th January following a serious
OL,11,Fincident, our out of hours
OL,12,Fhomelessness service continued to
OL,13,Fengage throughout the night with our
OL,14,Fpartner organisations to address
OL,15,Fissues of rough sleeping.''
